  "instructions": [
    "Heat the ceramic tagine over medium heat and drizzle in olive oil.",
    "Add diced onion and minced garlic, sauté until translucent.",
    "Stir in the diced aubergine and cook until lightly browned.",
    "Mix in smoked paprika, tomato paste, and dijon mustard, coating the vegetables evenly.",
    "Pour in broth, bring to a gentle simmer, cover, and cook for 20 minutes.",
